      • test_describeOptimizer_iri_and_var

        public void test_describeOptimizer_iri_and_var()
        Unit test for the AST rewrite of a simple describe query involving an IRI and a variable bound by a WHERE clause. The IRI in this case was chosen such that it would NOT be selected by the WHERE clause. 
         describe  ?x 
 where {
   ?x rdf:type foaf:Person
 }
        This test verifies that the correct CONSTRUCT clause is generated and that a WHERE clause is added which will capture the necessary bindings to support that CONSTUCT while preserving the original WHERE clause.

      • test_describeOptimizer_star

        public void test_describeOptimizer_star()
        DESCRIBE * is a short hand for all variables in the query. 
         describe * where { x rdf:type foaf:Person }

      • test_describeOptimizer_star_no_vars

        public void test_describeOptimizer_star_no_vars()
        This query is illegal since there are no variables to be described.
